oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: A.V.C. Lake Geneva Song Sheet
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: An original typed sheet containing the lyrics to three songs; two written by Jonnie Forrest and one by Langston Hughes. Also includes handwritten notations in pencil.
